---
const repoUrl = "https://github.com/vedanthvdev/dayseam";
const releasesUrl = `${repoUrl}/releases/latest`;
const codesignDoc = `${repoUrl}/blob/master/docs/release/CODESIGN.md`;
---

<section id="install" class="border-t border-slate-200/60 py-20 dark:border-slate-800">
  <div class="container-prose">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-white"
      >
        Install
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Grab the latest signed <code class="font-mono text-base">.dmg</code> from
        GitHub Releases. During public beta the first launch may still ask you to
        approve the app in System Settings &rarr; Privacy &amp; Security.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-seam-400/20 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-seam-700 dark:text-seam-300"
            >1</span
          >
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
            Download
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Pick the universal <code class="font-mono">.dmg</code> from the latest
          release. Apple Silicon and Intel are both supported.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-seam-400/20 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-seam-700 dark:text-seam-300"
            >2</span
          >
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
            Verify
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Each release ships with a minisign signature you can verify offline
          before opening the <code class="font-mono">.dmg</code>. The checksum and
          verification commands are on the release page.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span
            class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-seam-400/20 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-seam-700 dark:text-seam-300"
            >3</span
          >
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
            Connect a source
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          On first launch, add one of your tools (local Git, GitHub, GitLab, Jira,
          Confluence). Tokens are stored in macOS Keychain.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href={releasesUrl}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-slate-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-seam-500 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-slate-200"
      >
        Go to latest release
      </a>
      <a
        href={codesignDoc}
        class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-400 dark:decoration-slate-700 dark:hover:text-white"
      >
        Read the code-signing notes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
